author: Sanjith Sidhardhan
title: Dileep starts filming of King Liar
text:
King Liar has finally on the floors. The Dileep movie started filming on Tuesday in Kochi with its lead stars Dileep and Madonna Sebastian.
King Liar will see the hitmaking combo of Siddique and Lal team up after 16 years. The movie is touted to be an all-out entertainer and will be shot in Kochi, Kuttanad and Dubai.
Dileep meanwhile has finished with the filming of Two Countries , which has him uniting with Kalyanaraman director Shafi and My Boss co-star Mamta Mohandas.
